1. Ja sam *otpušten* iz posla prošlog meseca. (I was *fired* from my job last month.)
2. Oni su *otpustili* više radnika zbog smanjenja budžeta. (They *laid off* several employees due to budget cuts.)
3. Da li znate da li će Ivan biti *otpušten* nakon reorganizacije? (Do you know if Ivan will be *dismissed* after the reorganization?)
4. Sutradan su *otpustili* sve zaposlene iz te kancelarije. (They *released* all employees from that office the next day.)
5. Potrebno je da *otpustite* gas da bi krenuli. (You need to *release* the gas to start.)
6. Bolest mu nije dozvolila da bude *otpušten* iz bolnice ranije. (Illness prevented him from being *discharged* from the hospital earlier.)
7. Na kraju koncerta, publika je bila *otpusta* naizgled beskonačne povike. (At the end of the concert, the audience was *let go* seemingly endless cheers.)